    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Vegetable oil obtained from mustard seeds, characterized as a nondrying oil primarily used in food products, medicines, and a plasticizer with drying oils and with natural and synthetic resins.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
